Yes it is intentional

You can actually modify it by altering the engineAccelerationBaseSpeed in the engine module and reactorSpeedMult  in the reactor module

the applied formula is 

Engine.engineAccelerationSpeed = engineAccelerationBaseSpeed * reactorSpeedMult  
Engine.engineDecelerationSpeed = engineDecelerationBaseSpeed * (float)AttachedReactor.ReactorSpeedMult

and internally in KSP 

currentThrottle += (user throttle - currentThrottle) * engineAccelerationSpeed * dt
